title: Class President Strips at Assembly
description: A class president is trying so hard to get elected that she is willing to strip in front of an assembly. Only her shoes stay on. The quality is somewhat low, but not unwatchable. It looks like it was shot with a pocket-sized digital camera or a cell phone. There is a lot of wobbling, but the video itself is pretty clear - not bad at all for an audience recording of a live performance. WMV format.
